    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0002",
      "text": " 78",
      "bbox": [
        521.04,
        723.59,
        534.92,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0003",
      "text": "4.2.24.5  Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        214.86,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0004",
      "text": "LS_RJT: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        81.65,
        138.19,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0005",
      "text": "LS_RJT signifies the rejection of the RLIR Request",
      "bbox": [
        138.18,
        81.65,
        363.72,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0006",
      "text": "LS_ACC: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        105.64,
        142.05,
        116.76
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0007",
      "text": "LS_ACC signifies acceptance of the RLIR Request and its Link Incident Record.  The for-",
      "bbox": [
        142.08,
        105.64,
        540.13,
        116.76
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0008",
      "text": "mat of the LS_ACC Payload is shown in table 73.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        117.64,
        314.27,
        128.76
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0009",
      "text": "4.2.25",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        123.74,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0010",
      "text": "Link Incident Record Registration (LIRR)",
      "bbox": [
        133.74,
        226.96,
        326.49,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0011",
      "text": "4.2.25.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        192.63,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0012",
      "text": "See 4.2.24.1 for terms related to link incident reporting.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        339.32,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0013",
      "text": "The LIRR ELS requests the recipient to add or remove this source Nx_Port to or from the list of",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        540.03,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0014",
      "text": "Nx_Port’s registered to receive the Registered Link Incident Report (RLIR) ELS.  The normal re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        540.27,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0015",
      "text": "sponse to a LIRR ELS Sequence shall be a LS_ACC ELS Sequence with no Payload.  If the recipient",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        540.07,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0016",
      "text": "Nx_Port does not support the LIRR ELS, it shall reply with a LS_RJT ELS Sequence with a reason",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        539.87,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0017",
      "text": "code of \"Command not supported\".  If the recipient Nx_Port  is unable to perform the requested LIRR",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        540.0,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0018",
      "text": "registration function or the specified format is not supported, it shall reply with a LS_RJT ELS Se-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        540.03,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0019",
      "text": "quence with a reason code of \"Unable to perform command request\".",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        401.98,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0020",
      "text": "When an Nx_Port is registering or de-registering with the Fabric for receipt of Link Incident Records",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        540.03,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0021",
      "text": "from the Fabric, the LIRR ELS shall be sent to the Management Server (FFFFFAh).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        464.77,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0022",
      "text": "4.2.25.2  Registration for Link Incident Records",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        319.34,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0023",
      "text": "To obtain and process Link Incident Records, a ULP shall register it's port with other ports of interest.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        540.06,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0024",
      "text": "The term ’ports of interest’ refers to all ports that the registered port may address and for which the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        539.83,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0025",
      "text": "port requires their Link Incident Records.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        275.91,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0026",
      "text": "An Nx_Port shall attempt to register as a valid recipient of subsequent Link Incident Records by",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        540.03,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0027",
      "text": "sending a LIRR ELS as soon as the requesting Nx_Port has determined its address identifier and has",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        540.06,
        526.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0028",
      "text": "determined the address identifiers for the ports of interest.  The ULP shall indicate the format of Link",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        540.07,
        538.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0029",
      "text": "Incident Records of interest that are being registered.  The recipient Nx_Port shall respond with a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        539.87,
        550.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0030",
      "text": "LS_ACC ELS with no Payload.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        232.61,
        562.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0031",
      "text": "When a registered ULP is no longer interested in receiving Link Incident Records from any port or",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        539.96,
        586.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0032",
      "text": "ports of interest, it shall send a LIRR ELS to de-register their port as a valid recipient of Link Incident",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        540.07,
        598.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0033",
      "text": "Records.  The ULP shall indicate the format of Link Incident Records that are being de-registered.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        527.64,
        610.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0034",
      "text": "If a LIRR ELS requesting a de-registration function for a port that is not registered is received, the re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        539.98,
        634.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0035",
      "text": "cipient port accepts the request by sending a LS_ACC ELS and performs no further action.  If a LIRR",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        635.02,
        540.1,
        646.13
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0036",
      "text": "ELS requesting a registration for a port that is already registered for the specified format, the recipient",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        540.09,
        658.13
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0037",
      "text": "port shall accept by sending a LS_ACC ELS request and perform no further action.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        462.0,
        670.13
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0038",
      "text": "The recipient of a LIRR ELS shall maintain a separate established registration list of valid Link Inci-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        683.02,
        540.04,
        694.13
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p097_s0039",
      "text": "dent Record recipients for each registration format specified.  The size of the established registration",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        695.02,
        540.03,
        706.13
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
